Module mesakit.map.region
Package com.telenav.mesakit.map.region

Class RegionIdentity

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.map.region.RegionIdentity
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoSerializable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.Stringable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.StringSource
public class RegionIdentity extends Object implements com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.Stringable, com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoSerializable

Holds all coding information about an MesaKit Region.

All regions are assigned an MesaKit region code as well as an ISO code or a synthetic ISO code. 

 [world]

  mesakit: World
  iso: WORLD

 [continent]

  mesakit: Oceania
  iso: OC

 [time-zone]

  iso: America/Seattle

 [country]

  mesakit: United_States
  iso: US

 [country]-[state]

  mesakit: Mexico-Aguascalientes
  iso: MX-AG

 [country]-[state]-Metro_[metro]

  mesakit: United_States-Washington-Metro_Seattle
  iso: US-WA-METRO_SEATTLE

 [country]-[state]-County_[county]

  mesakit:United_States-Washington-County_King
  iso: US-WA-COUNTY_KING

 [country]-[state]-City_[city]

  mesakit: United_States-Washington-City_Seattle
  iso: US-WA-CITY_SEATTLE

 [country]-[state]-City-[city]-District_[district]
  mesakit: United_States-Washington-City_Seattle-District_Green_Lake
  iso: US-WA-CITY_SEATTLE-DISTRICT_GREEN_LAKE
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
